WEBVTT

00:01:40.830 --> 00:01:46.020
[THE DEVIL BETWEEN US]

00:01:46.080 --> 00:01:48.930
[Episode 13]

00:02:36.310 --> 00:02:38.310
I'm heading back to the repair shop.

00:04:00.060 --> 00:04:02.520
I thought Cao Jinchuan
had already run away.

00:04:04.560 --> 00:04:05.430
Who knew he would

00:04:05.430 --> 00:04:07.290
suddenly show up at my door today,

00:04:07.330 --> 00:04:08.560
ask for money,

00:04:09.480 --> 00:04:11.080
and threaten me with Jiajia?

00:04:14.030 --> 00:04:15.160
You killed someone.

00:04:15.260 --> 00:04:16.920
He threatened me with Jiajia.

00:04:26.800 --> 00:04:27.510
Where are we driving to?

00:04:27.510 --> 00:04:28.680
Can't we go somewhere closer?

00:04:28.680 --> 00:04:31.340
I'm worried about
leaving the kid alone at home.

00:04:40.800 --> 00:04:41.560
Do you know

00:04:41.560 --> 00:04:43.360
how serious this is?

00:04:44.720 --> 00:04:47.110
Cao Jinchuan is connected to the buyer.

00:04:47.440 --> 00:04:48.900
Now that the buyer is dead,

00:04:49.090 --> 00:04:50.750
the police will definitely find him.

00:04:50.750 --> 00:04:52.830
Can you guarantee
that no one saw Cao Jinchuan

00:04:52.830 --> 00:04:54.030
coming to your house?

00:04:55.560 --> 00:04:56.760
If the police show up,

00:04:56.870 --> 00:04:57.800
what will you do?

00:05:03.560 --> 00:05:04.310
Right now, besides us,

00:05:04.310 --> 00:05:05.910
no one knows where Xiaoyu is.

00:05:06.940 --> 00:05:08.540
The goods aren't at my place.

00:05:09.560 --> 00:05:11.290
Once we get rid of Cao Jinchuan,

00:05:14.480 --> 00:05:15.600
even if the police come knocking,

00:05:15.600 --> 00:05:16.800
they won't get anything out of me.

00:05:16.800 --> 00:05:18.660
They won't get anything from you,

00:05:18.680 --> 00:05:19.350
but what about Jiajia?

00:05:19.350 --> 00:05:20.810
I'll teach her what to say.

00:05:22.210 --> 00:05:23.140
Jiajia is smart.

00:05:25.510 --> 00:05:26.720
There are too many holes in this.

00:05:26.720 --> 00:05:28.250
This is our only option now.

00:05:32.460 --> 00:05:33.820
No one else can

00:05:34.340 --> 00:05:35.750
know about Cao Jinchuan.

00:05:41.120 --> 00:05:42.870
I won't tell Xiaoya about this.

00:05:44.650 --> 00:05:47.340
The success of the slimming pill sales
depends on this.

00:05:47.340 --> 00:05:49.270
She can't be distracted right now.

00:05:50.380 --> 00:05:52.310
We are racing against the police.

00:05:53.570 --> 00:05:55.159
This business won't last long.

00:05:55.159 --> 00:05:56.159
Once we make the money and split it,

00:05:56.159 --> 00:05:57.320
Xiaoya and I will go abroad.

00:05:57.320 --> 00:05:59.320
Think about what you should do next.

00:05:59.370 --> 00:06:01.050
When things hit rock bottom,

00:06:01.750 --> 00:06:02.950
what else can you do?

00:06:53.740 --> 00:06:54.450
Dong,

00:06:55.500 --> 00:06:57.180
if it comes to that,

00:06:58.850 --> 00:07:00.580
you have to take care of Jiajia.

00:07:01.430 --> 00:07:02.870
If that really happens,

00:07:05.530 --> 00:07:07.330
I won't be far from death either.

00:07:18.070 --> 00:07:18.750
Yu,

00:07:18.990 --> 00:07:20.320
keep an eye on that side.

00:07:20.440 --> 00:07:20.960
Liang,

00:07:20.980 --> 00:07:21.910
watch the upstairs.

00:07:21.910 --> 00:07:22.350
Kai,

00:07:22.380 --> 00:07:23.380
watch over there.

00:07:23.480 --> 00:07:24.310
How about this, Jie?

00:07:24.310 --> 00:07:25.680
You take your men back first.

00:07:25.680 --> 00:07:26.560
That's it for today.

00:07:26.560 --> 00:07:27.760
Okay, we'll head out.

00:07:27.770 --> 00:07:28.690
Good work, everyone.

00:07:28.690 --> 00:07:29.210
Okay.

00:07:29.720 --> 00:07:30.240
We'll switch shifts tomorrow.

00:07:30.240 --> 00:07:30.890
Good work.

00:07:31.190 --> 00:07:32.990
You should go back with them too.

00:07:35.680 --> 00:07:36.610
You startled me.

00:07:37.190 --> 00:07:37.920
Let's go.

00:07:37.920 --> 00:07:38.780
It's this late.

00:07:38.860 --> 00:07:40.560
Just the two of you
staring at each other here.

00:07:40.560 --> 00:07:41.690
We're just leaving?

00:07:42.550 --> 00:07:43.970
Either he's not coming back,

00:07:43.970 --> 00:07:45.530
or he's already spotted us.

00:07:45.800 --> 00:07:47.310
I've left three people here to keep watch.

00:07:47.310 --> 00:07:48.430
Let's go back and rest.

00:07:48.430 --> 00:07:49.950
We'll continue searching tomorrow.

00:07:49.950 --> 00:07:50.480
Wenjing.

00:07:51.080 --> 00:07:51.610
Let's go.

00:07:52.400 --> 00:07:53.080
Let's go.

00:09:14.330 --> 00:09:15.210
[Nuanfeng Hengke Electronics Co., Ltd.]

00:09:45.960 --> 00:09:46.750
I worked overtime today,

00:09:46.750 --> 00:09:47.680
so I'm back late.

00:09:59.910 --> 00:10:01.710
Why aren't you saying anything?

00:10:03.750 --> 00:10:05.210
You haven't eaten, right?

00:10:08.750 --> 00:10:10.680
I'll make you something right now.

00:10:37.670 --> 00:10:41.130
I finally understand
why you didn't call the police last time.

00:10:44.270 --> 00:10:45.440
It's not what you think.

00:10:45.440 --> 00:10:46.370
Did you eat this?

00:10:52.710 --> 00:10:54.430
I promised you in rehab

00:10:54.780 --> 00:10:55.970
that I could quit.

00:10:57.070 --> 00:10:58.000
And I did.

00:10:59.280 --> 00:11:00.140
What about you?

00:11:08.410 --> 00:11:09.320
I can quit.

00:11:11.460 --> 00:11:12.820
I definitely can.

00:11:13.580 --> 00:11:14.780
Where did you just go?

00:11:21.270 --> 00:11:21.630
I...

00:11:21.630 --> 00:11:22.960
I was working overtime.

00:11:25.720 --> 00:11:26.850
You're still lying.

00:11:30.140 --> 00:11:32.800
I saw you get into
that man's car with my own eyes.

00:11:41.610 --> 00:11:42.810
I didn't tell you.

00:11:46.020 --> 00:11:47.330
I'm dating him.

00:11:54.240 --> 00:11:54.930
Good.

00:11:58.160 --> 00:11:58.870
Very good.

00:12:04.140 --> 00:12:05.270
I called the police.

00:12:07.100 --> 00:12:08.670
Hu Wenjing will be here soon.

00:12:08.670 --> 00:12:10.800
Your boyfriend won't get away either.

00:12:17.650 --> 00:12:18.910
You called the police?

00:12:25.190 --> 00:12:26.550
Why would you do that?

00:12:28.180 --> 00:12:30.910
Do you know this time
is different from last time?

00:12:31.110 --> 00:12:32.870
If the factory finds out, I'll be fired.

00:12:32.870 --> 00:12:35.000
How can I support you without a salary?

00:12:35.180 --> 00:12:36.730
Do you even care about me?

00:12:38.200 --> 00:12:39.990
I could quit drugs for you.

00:12:41.030 --> 00:12:41.890
What about you?

00:12:42.320 --> 00:12:43.720
You're such a hypocrite.

00:12:44.440 --> 00:12:46.030
Full of lies.

00:12:47.090 --> 00:12:48.680
Letting yourself rot.

00:13:02.790 --> 00:13:03.480
Wang An.

00:13:06.590 --> 00:13:08.460
Anyone else can say that about me,

00:13:10.760 --> 00:13:12.160
but not you.

00:13:15.720 --> 00:13:17.240
Do you have a conscience?

00:13:20.550 --> 00:13:22.010
I went to school and worked

00:13:22.960 --> 00:13:24.120
at the same time.

00:13:25.470 --> 00:13:27.400
I raised you since you were little.

00:13:28.390 --> 00:13:30.440
I was both a sister

00:13:31.270 --> 00:13:32.630
and a mother to you.

00:13:32.900 --> 00:13:34.500
You're 25 years old,

00:13:35.510 --> 00:13:37.150
and you haven't earned a cent.

00:13:37.150 --> 00:13:39.630
I feed you and take care of you,

00:13:39.630 --> 00:13:42.120
and I've never complained.

00:13:42.550 --> 00:13:45.120
If you hadn't brought that stuff home,

00:13:45.320 --> 00:13:47.080
how could I have taken it?

00:13:47.360 --> 00:13:50.480
I would never have touched it in my life!

00:13:50.480 --> 00:13:51.600
Right?

00:13:51.960 --> 00:13:54.080
I would never have had the chance

00:13:54.080 --> 00:13:55.270
to touch that stuff.

00:13:55.630 --> 00:13:58.150
How could you say that to me?

00:13:58.840 --> 00:14:00.320
How could you?

00:14:09.330 --> 00:14:10.780
Look at yourself now.

00:14:11.240 --> 00:14:12.570
Are you still Wang Ping?

00:14:16.390 --> 00:14:17.390
Look at yourself.

00:14:20.870 --> 00:14:22.800
You're talking to me like this now?

00:14:25.360 --> 00:14:26.600
Am I Wang Ping?

00:14:29.510 --> 00:14:30.480
Am I?

00:14:34.260 --> 00:14:37.660
Even if I overdose on this stuff and die,

00:14:39.040 --> 00:14:40.670
I'm still your sister.

00:15:07.750 --> 00:15:08.600
Wang Ping.

00:15:16.550 --> 00:15:18.080
Where did you get the drugs?

00:15:30.290 --> 00:15:30.910
Police! Freeze!

00:15:30.910 --> 00:15:31.440
Freeze!

00:15:31.720 --> 00:15:32.200
Hands on your head!

00:15:32.200 --> 00:15:32.840
Hands on your head!

00:15:32.840 --> 00:15:33.440
Freeze!

00:15:33.790 --> 00:15:36.270
We are now summoning you
in accordance with the law.

00:15:36.270 --> 00:15:37.070
Take him away.

00:15:39.720 --> 00:15:40.500
Start talking.

00:15:40.500 --> 00:15:42.030
Where did you buy the drugs?

00:15:44.630 --> 00:15:46.270
I bought them from Quan's place.

00:15:46.270 --> 00:15:47.510
Quan is already dead.

00:15:48.030 --> 00:15:49.120
I know.

00:15:49.560 --> 00:15:52.820
Can't I have bought them
before something happened to him?

00:15:55.840 --> 00:15:58.140
We found 15 kilogs of hallucinogen-laced

00:15:58.140 --> 00:15:59.940
candy in your house.

00:16:00.460 --> 00:16:03.120
Who were you planning to sell
all those drugs to?

00:16:03.460 --> 00:16:04.860
Don't accuse me falsely.

00:16:05.390 --> 00:16:07.240
I bought it all for personal use.

00:16:07.700 --> 00:16:08.870
I never sell it.

00:16:09.270 --> 00:16:10.820
If you don't believe me, ask Wang Ping

00:16:10.820 --> 00:16:12.420
if I ever took a cent from her.

00:16:13.030 --> 00:16:13.790
Besides,

00:16:13.790 --> 00:16:16.670
the drug content
in those candies is very low.

00:16:17.110 --> 00:16:18.630
Fifteen kilograms

00:16:18.790 --> 00:16:20.080
sounds dramatic.

00:16:20.310 --> 00:16:22.420
How much could you
actually extract from that?

00:16:22.420 --> 00:16:24.970
You can't convict me of drug trafficking,

00:16:25.000 --> 00:16:27.530
nor can you convict me
of illegal possession.

00:16:28.000 --> 00:16:29.440
At most, you can detain me for a few days.

00:16:29.440 --> 00:16:31.170
You think you know the law, huh?

00:16:32.150 --> 00:16:34.390
You lured and instigated
others to use drugs.

00:16:34.390 --> 00:16:37.320
That's three to seven years in prison.
You know that?

00:16:37.600 --> 00:16:39.400
Didn't you instigate Wang Ping?

00:16:39.490 --> 00:16:40.550
How did I instigate her?

00:16:40.550 --> 00:16:41.510
You tell me how you did it.

00:16:41.510 --> 00:16:42.200
Do you have evidence?

00:16:42.200 --> 00:16:42.870
I do.

00:16:45.320 --> 00:16:48.510
Wang Ping using before
had nothing to do with me, right?

00:16:49.390 --> 00:16:51.440
Later, she couldn't resist relapsing.

00:16:51.440 --> 00:16:52.440
She knew I had candy,

00:16:52.440 --> 00:16:53.870
so she came crying and begging me.

00:16:53.870 --> 00:16:55.080
What could I do?

00:16:56.270 --> 00:16:58.270
You know your colleague
Li Jingjing, right?

00:16:58.270 --> 00:16:59.630
Li Jingjing told us

00:16:59.750 --> 00:17:01.550
that you once asked her
to give Wang Ping a cup of coffee.

00:17:01.550 --> 00:17:02.120
Right?

00:17:02.480 --> 00:17:03.600
What was in that coffee?

00:17:03.600 --> 00:17:04.829
You know very well.

00:17:05.880 --> 00:17:06.920
You counted on

00:17:06.920 --> 00:17:08.349
Wang Ping's history with drugs

00:17:08.349 --> 00:17:09.240
to control her.

00:17:10.920 --> 00:17:11.530
Li.

00:17:12.030 --> 00:17:12.920
Come here.

00:17:14.790 --> 00:17:15.310
Mr. Han.

00:17:15.310 --> 00:17:15.839
Um,

00:17:15.869 --> 00:17:18.329
Wang Ping's been
in a bad mood lately, right?

00:17:19.369 --> 00:17:19.960
Here.

00:17:20.230 --> 00:17:21.560
Take this coffee to her.

00:17:29.680 --> 00:17:30.480
Ping.

00:17:32.690 --> 00:17:33.380
Here.

00:17:38.480 --> 00:17:39.240
For me?

00:17:39.640 --> 00:17:40.240
It's okay.

00:17:40.510 --> 00:17:41.310
Ignore them.

00:17:41.620 --> 00:17:42.420
Hang in there.

00:18:04.450 --> 00:18:06.100
Can I have another ten?

00:18:07.200 --> 00:18:08.410
Five works too.

00:18:09.210 --> 00:18:11.340
You're eating them faster and faster.

00:18:11.930 --> 00:18:13.520
I'll try to control myself.

00:18:13.910 --> 00:18:15.390
I can't just keep

00:18:15.550 --> 00:18:17.230
supplying you for free.

00:18:18.030 --> 00:18:19.430
Get off work early today.

00:18:21.070 --> 00:18:23.000
I'll wait for you at the same place.

00:18:29.270 --> 00:18:30.240
I want a lawyer.

00:18:30.380 --> 00:18:31.970
You don't get to decide everything.

00:18:31.970 --> 00:18:33.170
Don't get cocky here.

00:18:41.370 --> 00:18:42.040
Kai.

00:18:46.590 --> 00:18:47.320
You go ahead.

00:18:47.510 --> 00:18:48.070
Are you okay?

00:18:48.070 --> 00:18:48.600
I'm fine.

00:18:58.710 --> 00:18:59.910
Do you know Li Baocai?

00:19:00.010 --> 00:19:00.820
No.

00:19:01.850 --> 00:19:02.720
What about Cao Jinchuan?

00:19:02.720 --> 00:19:03.400
No.

00:19:04.080 --> 00:19:06.810
Where were you on the night
of the 20th last month?

00:19:07.400 --> 00:19:09.940
Either drinking with friends
or playing cards.

00:19:09.940 --> 00:19:11.140
Let me remind you.

00:19:11.790 --> 00:19:12.830
On the 20th,

00:19:12.830 --> 00:19:15.070
there was a murder in Wujing Village.

00:19:15.440 --> 00:19:17.350
A bag of drugs was found at the scene.

00:19:17.350 --> 00:19:18.270
Its composition matches

00:19:18.270 --> 00:19:20.350
the candy you've been stockpiling.

00:19:20.590 --> 00:19:22.000
We have reason to suspect

00:19:22.000 --> 00:19:24.000
that you're connected to this case.

00:19:26.190 --> 00:19:27.630
Don't throw dirt on me.

00:19:28.200 --> 00:19:29.720
Wujing Village?

00:19:29.720 --> 00:19:30.550
I've never been there.

00:19:30.550 --> 00:19:32.280
Never even heard of that place.

00:19:34.580 --> 00:19:35.530
I remember now.

00:19:35.590 --> 00:19:36.360
On the 20th,

00:19:36.840 --> 00:19:38.180
I was playing cards
with a bunch of friends.

00:19:38.180 --> 00:19:38.890
There were many people.

00:19:38.890 --> 00:19:40.150
You can investigate it.

00:19:40.150 --> 00:19:42.350
Are they your card buddies
or drug buddies?

00:19:42.350 --> 00:19:43.400
Card buddies, of course.

00:19:43.400 --> 00:19:45.400
I don't know that many drug addicts.

00:19:46.070 --> 00:19:47.790
You hoarded so many drugs in your house

00:19:47.790 --> 00:19:49.110
and you say you don't sell them.

00:19:49.110 --> 00:19:50.440
Who would believe that?

00:19:50.990 --> 00:19:52.070
That's because

00:19:52.110 --> 00:19:54.270
Quan could get me receipts.

00:19:54.270 --> 00:19:55.240
No matter how much I bought,

00:19:55.240 --> 00:19:56.880
the factory reimbursed me.

00:19:57.370 --> 00:19:59.240
It didn't cost me a cent.

00:19:59.590 --> 00:20:00.920
Why would I spend so much

00:20:00.920 --> 00:20:02.250
of my own money to buy it?

00:20:06.860 --> 00:20:07.730
Han Qiang.

00:20:09.490 --> 00:20:10.820
I'm giving you a chance now.

00:20:10.820 --> 00:20:12.070
Think it over carefully.

00:20:12.070 --> 00:20:12.570
I...

00:20:19.070 --> 00:20:21.070
I'm telling the truth, Officer.

00:20:23.240 --> 00:20:23.720
Well...

00:20:23.880 --> 00:20:25.880
I'm telling you to think carefully.

00:20:28.230 --> 00:20:28.990
Are you okay?

00:20:33.580 --> 00:20:35.440
When Wang Ping's parents died

00:20:35.440 --> 00:20:36.640
in that car accident,

00:20:37.200 --> 00:20:39.460
we were in our senior year of high school.

00:20:40.310 --> 00:20:42.030
Wang Ping changed after that.

00:20:43.880 --> 00:20:45.400
She lived frugally on

00:20:47.160 --> 00:20:49.020
that little compensation money.

00:20:52.100 --> 00:20:54.830
It wasn't easy for her
to get to where she is today.

00:20:56.510 --> 00:20:57.970
And drugs ruined it all.

00:21:05.250 --> 00:21:06.650
We have new information.

00:21:12.390 --> 00:21:13.000
Um,

00:21:13.400 --> 00:21:14.110
officers,

00:21:14.920 --> 00:21:16.180
if what I'm about to say

00:21:16.180 --> 00:21:17.350
is useful,

00:21:17.600 --> 00:21:19.200
will it count as meritorious service?

00:21:19.200 --> 00:21:20.110
Say it first.

00:21:20.720 --> 00:21:21.240
Okay.

00:21:22.350 --> 00:21:25.550
That Cao Jinchuan you just mentioned—

00:21:25.920 --> 00:21:26.780
I remember him.

00:21:27.270 --> 00:21:28.160
Cao Jinchuan!

00:21:29.160 --> 00:21:29.880
Don't run!

00:21:32.470 --> 00:21:34.070
What kind of person
called out to Cao Jinchuan?

00:21:34.070 --> 00:21:35.270
I didn't get a good look.

00:21:35.270 --> 00:21:37.310
He just flashed right past me.

00:21:37.310 --> 00:21:38.200
It was too fast.

00:21:40.070 --> 00:21:42.320
We've been to
the mahjong parlor you mentioned.

00:21:42.320 --> 00:21:44.650
The owner didn't mention this lead at all.

00:21:44.900 --> 00:21:46.420
Maybe he forgot.

00:21:46.800 --> 00:21:48.600
Or maybe he didn't want trouble.

00:21:49.200 --> 00:21:50.400
I wasn't the only one there that day.

00:21:50.400 --> 00:21:51.310
There were many people.

00:21:51.310 --> 00:21:52.440
You can go ask them.

00:21:52.460 --> 00:21:53.460
We'll ask.

00:22:04.130 --> 00:22:05.310
[Xiaoya Recommends New Diet Pills]

00:22:05.820 --> 00:22:06.410
Let me see.

00:22:06.410 --> 00:22:07.470
How did it turn out?

00:22:08.400 --> 00:22:09.680
How come you're so thin lately?

00:22:09.680 --> 00:22:10.310
Really?

00:22:10.310 --> 00:22:10.420
Your face looks so small
even in the front.

00:22:10.420 --> 00:22:11.510
[I must lose weight this time.]

00:22:11.510 --> 00:22:12.640
What's your secret?

00:22:12.680 --> 00:22:15.480
I recently found a miracle product.

00:22:15.480 --> 00:22:15.640
[I want to try it too.]

00:22:15.640 --> 00:22:16.670
With this little thing,

00:22:16.670 --> 00:22:17.110
[I lost 10 kilos with this.]

00:22:17.110 --> 00:22:19.000
you can eat whatever you want all day.

00:22:19.000 --> 00:22:20.510
[Visitors; Sales; Total orders]

00:22:20.510 --> 00:22:21.920
No matter how much you eat,

00:22:21.920 --> 00:22:22.390
you won't gain weight.

00:22:22.390 --> 00:22:23.200
[So happy.]

00:22:23.200 --> 00:22:24.070
Plus,

00:22:24.070 --> 00:22:25.880
just one pack a day,

00:22:25.880 --> 00:22:26.270
[I've lost weight. I need to order more.]

00:22:26.270 --> 00:22:28.590
you don't just maintain,
you actually drop.

00:22:28.590 --> 00:22:29.310
It works so well?

00:22:29.310 --> 00:22:29.920
For real?

00:22:29.920 --> 00:22:30.680
Yeah.

00:22:30.830 --> 00:22:32.070
I want to try it too.

00:22:35.640 --> 00:22:36.930
Thanks for your hard work, Chao.

00:22:36.930 --> 00:22:37.930
Don't mention it.

00:22:39.160 --> 00:22:39.790
Thank you.

00:22:40.010 --> 00:22:40.690
Take care.

00:23:02.790 --> 00:23:05.120
Do you know
what our turnover is right now?

00:23:05.220 --> 00:23:05.940
How much?

00:23:10.360 --> 00:23:11.740
2.38 million.

00:23:13.550 --> 00:23:14.750
The gross profit rate

00:23:15.770 --> 00:23:17.490
is as high as 95%.

00:23:23.980 --> 00:23:25.110
We're rich.

00:23:26.470 --> 00:23:27.160
We made it.

00:23:27.790 --> 00:23:29.070
We're loaded!

00:23:29.240 --> 00:23:31.470
We made it.

00:23:33.790 --> 00:23:34.960
Why isn't he happy?

00:23:35.210 --> 00:23:35.770
Happy.

00:23:37.000 --> 00:23:37.550
I'm happy.

00:23:37.550 --> 00:23:38.750
Doesn't look like it.

00:23:40.200 --> 00:23:41.330
I've figured it out.

00:23:41.750 --> 00:23:42.830
I've been thinking for the past few days.

00:23:42.830 --> 00:23:44.960
We can set up a membership system.

00:23:45.340 --> 00:23:47.340
1,888 for junior membership.

00:23:47.520 --> 00:23:49.170
Free pills for three months.

00:23:49.550 --> 00:23:50.950
5-kilo loss guaranteed.

00:23:50.950 --> 00:23:53.010
5,888 for intermediate membership.

00:23:53.550 --> 00:23:55.010
25-kilo loss guaranteed.

00:23:55.290 --> 00:23:57.420
18,888 for senior membership.

00:23:57.590 --> 00:23:58.790
Free pills for life.

00:23:58.790 --> 00:23:59.960
No rebound ever.

00:24:00.070 --> 00:24:01.480
We need to ride this wave,

00:24:01.480 --> 00:24:02.750
make the most money

00:24:02.770 --> 00:24:04.020
in the fastest speed.

00:24:04.750 --> 00:24:05.310
Okay?

00:24:05.480 --> 00:24:06.140
Okay. Good.

00:24:06.240 --> 00:24:06.770
Alright.

00:24:09.070 --> 00:24:09.830
So roughly

00:24:10.070 --> 00:24:11.270
when exactly can we

00:24:11.270 --> 00:24:12.510
get our dividends?

00:24:14.240 --> 00:24:15.310
We've only just started.

00:24:15.310 --> 00:24:16.110
Still early.

00:24:18.750 --> 00:24:20.270
Can I take one million in advance?

00:24:20.270 --> 00:24:21.330
I need it urgently.

00:24:22.960 --> 00:24:23.750
No.

00:24:25.030 --> 00:24:26.750
Packaging, production, marketing—

00:24:26.750 --> 00:24:28.070
they all cost money.

00:24:28.880 --> 00:24:30.350
This is like a snowball.

00:24:30.640 --> 00:24:32.720
We need to reinvest the money we make.

00:24:33.310 --> 00:24:34.480
If you pull money out now,

00:24:34.480 --> 00:24:35.770
our accounts will be messed up.

00:24:35.770 --> 00:24:37.170
Just wait a few more days.

00:24:37.350 --> 00:24:38.400
I can't wait now, Xiaoya.

00:24:38.400 --> 00:24:39.240
It's really urgent.

00:24:39.240 --> 00:24:39.960
Ken,

00:24:41.340 --> 00:24:43.740
didn't we agree
that I manage the accounts?

00:24:43.900 --> 00:24:45.760
I really can't give you the money.

00:24:47.200 --> 00:24:47.960
I know.

00:24:49.200 --> 00:24:51.660
You want to help Jiajia
with her transplant.

00:24:51.790 --> 00:24:52.880
But you have to think it through.

00:24:52.880 --> 00:24:54.740
What about Jiajia's future life?

00:24:55.750 --> 00:24:57.150
You've lost your job now.

00:24:57.360 --> 00:24:59.480
And we're doing this kind of business.

00:24:59.480 --> 00:25:00.270
If you don't make a big score,

00:25:00.270 --> 00:25:02.600
how will you support Jiajia in the future?

00:25:03.680 --> 00:25:05.030
Don't worry. In a few days,

00:25:05.030 --> 00:25:06.760
I'll definitely give it to you.

00:25:06.830 --> 00:25:07.510
I promise.

00:25:14.510 --> 00:25:16.170
I've sorted all the receipts.

00:25:16.590 --> 00:25:18.590
Jiajia needs dialysis tomorrow.

00:25:18.590 --> 00:25:20.270
I won't come over.

00:25:20.290 --> 00:25:22.570
You'd better not
come at all in the future.

00:25:22.570 --> 00:25:23.700
Keep your distance.

00:25:25.780 --> 00:25:26.980
We have enough stock.

00:25:27.430 --> 00:25:29.270
The two of us can handle the shipping.

00:25:29.270 --> 00:25:31.350
Let's reduce contact

00:25:31.750 --> 00:25:32.750
to lower the risk.

00:25:34.590 --> 00:25:35.130
Ken,

00:25:35.510 --> 00:25:36.800
listen to Xiaoya.

00:25:39.150 --> 00:25:40.080
I'll see you out.

00:25:41.370 --> 00:25:42.130
So...

00:25:43.080 --> 00:25:44.920
we have a deal on the money?

00:25:45.750 --> 00:25:46.310
Even if you don't trust me,

00:25:46.310 --> 00:25:47.550
don't you trust him?

00:25:48.460 --> 00:25:49.390
Don't worry.

00:25:52.000 --> 00:25:52.550
If you need me,

00:25:52.550 --> 00:25:53.790
contact me the way I told you.

00:25:53.790 --> 00:25:54.310
Okay.

00:26:00.300 --> 00:26:01.170
I'm off.

00:26:02.070 --> 00:26:02.880
Take care.

00:26:07.040 --> 00:26:08.900
My brother's had enough bad luck.

00:26:09.000 --> 00:26:10.460
You won't scam him, right?

00:26:10.480 --> 00:26:11.510
Why would I scam him?

00:26:11.510 --> 00:26:13.370
What does he have worth scamming?

00:26:13.670 --> 00:26:14.780
Use your brain.

00:26:15.590 --> 00:26:17.400
An unemployed factory accountant

00:26:17.400 --> 00:26:19.190
suddenly coming up with a million.

00:26:19.190 --> 00:26:20.450
That screams trouble.

00:26:20.880 --> 00:26:22.340
It's asking for problems.

00:26:23.030 --> 00:26:23.790
Better

00:26:24.110 --> 00:26:25.040
wait until we've

00:26:25.440 --> 00:26:26.720
made enough money,

00:26:27.270 --> 00:26:28.730
when we're about to leave,

00:26:28.770 --> 00:26:29.960
then give him his cut.

00:26:29.960 --> 00:26:31.220
That's the safest way.

00:26:37.580 --> 00:26:39.980
You're thinking more and more thoroughly.

00:26:42.400 --> 00:26:44.400
You asked me to manage the accounts.

00:26:45.880 --> 00:26:47.080
How the money's made,

00:26:47.270 --> 00:26:48.530
how it should be split—

00:26:48.920 --> 00:26:50.980
of course I have to manage it clearly.

00:26:51.260 --> 00:26:52.440
I don't want anything.

00:26:52.440 --> 00:26:53.300
I only want you.

00:27:06.360 --> 00:27:08.490
My family built this house ourselves.

00:27:08.880 --> 00:27:10.610
Solid materials, top quality.

00:27:11.110 --> 00:27:12.310
Only my sister and I lived here,

00:27:12.310 --> 00:27:13.590
growing up together.

00:27:13.720 --> 00:27:15.120
So we took good care of it.

00:27:15.130 --> 00:27:16.460
It's well-maintained.

00:27:21.960 --> 00:27:23.650
Even when times were hard,

00:27:25.090 --> 00:27:26.820
we never thought of selling it.

00:27:29.880 --> 00:27:31.070
May I ask,

00:27:31.070 --> 00:27:32.790
why are you selling it now?

00:27:39.160 --> 00:27:40.030
My sister died.

00:27:57.350 --> 00:27:58.550
Has Wang An been here?

00:28:07.340 --> 00:28:08.380
Hang in there.

00:28:10.790 --> 00:28:12.590
You haven't been using for long.

00:28:13.750 --> 00:28:15.680
You'll definitely be able to quit.

00:28:22.670 --> 00:28:24.840
Han Qiang has already been arrested.

00:28:25.350 --> 00:28:26.590
So when you get out,

00:28:26.830 --> 00:28:28.760
no worries about running into him.

00:28:45.400 --> 00:28:46.310
Wang Ping.

00:28:48.240 --> 00:28:50.640
Don't you have anything
you want to tell me?

00:28:55.240 --> 00:28:56.640
What is Xiaoya busy with?

00:28:58.100 --> 00:28:59.560
She's busy with business.

00:29:00.200 --> 00:29:02.330
Her business has been booming lately,

00:29:02.750 --> 00:29:03.720
keeping her busy.

00:29:03.720 --> 00:29:05.660
I see the delivery trucks downstairs

00:29:05.660 --> 00:29:06.770
keep coming.

00:29:08.510 --> 00:29:09.590
Good for her.

00:29:21.440 --> 00:29:22.140
Wang Ping.

00:29:25.580 --> 00:29:28.240
Every addict, every dealer
in Nuanfeng County—

00:29:28.830 --> 00:29:30.680
I'll drag them out one by one.

00:29:31.880 --> 00:29:32.940
I promise you that.

00:29:38.770 --> 00:29:40.060
I'm already like this.

00:29:42.880 --> 00:29:44.280
There's no turning back.

00:29:47.480 --> 00:29:49.350
You can start over after you get out.

00:29:49.350 --> 00:29:50.160
You can do it.

00:29:57.600 --> 00:29:59.200
You still have me, Wang Ping.

00:30:16.760 --> 00:30:17.560
What's wrong?

00:30:17.960 --> 00:30:19.360
Get in. Let's get to work.

00:30:33.790 --> 00:30:34.790
That day,

00:30:34.820 --> 00:30:36.070
he just stood at the door

00:30:36.070 --> 00:30:37.120
and shouted.

00:30:37.350 --> 00:30:38.400
When my colleague came that day,

00:30:38.400 --> 00:30:39.860
why didn't you mention it?

00:30:40.440 --> 00:30:41.270
I forgot.

00:30:42.490 --> 00:30:44.220
Do you have surveillance here?

00:30:44.270 --> 00:30:44.850
No.

00:30:54.100 --> 00:30:55.430
Around what time was it?

00:30:56.260 --> 00:30:58.190
Probably around lunch time.

00:30:58.370 --> 00:31:00.170
I don't remember the exact time.

00:31:18.690 --> 00:31:19.570
Sir, pause here.

00:31:19.570 --> 00:31:20.370
Stop.

00:31:21.050 --> 00:31:22.490
Rewind a little bit.

00:31:25.580 --> 00:31:26.240
Right here.

00:31:27.510 --> 00:31:28.200
Zoom in.

00:31:28.200 --> 00:31:28.930
Zoom in a bit.

00:31:29.260 --> 00:31:30.460
Zoom in more. Closer.

00:31:35.350 --> 00:31:36.980
Is that Cheng Ken?

00:31:37.490 --> 00:31:38.050
Yes.

00:31:44.630 --> 00:31:47.800
Can we go see Jiang later?

00:31:49.650 --> 00:31:51.130
Not today.

00:31:51.550 --> 00:31:53.750
Jiang hasn't been feeling well lately.

00:31:54.590 --> 00:31:56.320
Uncle Xue is probably busy too.

00:31:57.070 --> 00:31:57.800
Another day.

00:31:58.960 --> 00:32:01.440
Xiaoyu hasn't been around lately.

00:32:01.590 --> 00:32:02.750
Neither have you.

00:32:03.070 --> 00:32:04.710
I'm always alone.

00:32:11.990 --> 00:32:12.800
Alright.

00:32:21.570 --> 00:32:23.370
Didn't we agree

00:32:24.370 --> 00:32:26.390
not to mention Xiaoyu anymore?

00:32:28.820 --> 00:32:30.100
I'm sorry.

00:32:35.890 --> 00:32:37.690
I won't be going out for work for a while.

00:32:37.690 --> 00:32:39.020
I'll stay home with you.

00:32:40.110 --> 00:32:41.260
Really?

00:32:41.350 --> 00:32:41.970
Really.

00:32:47.310 --> 00:32:47.960
Come on.

00:32:48.170 --> 00:32:48.930
Put this on.

00:32:57.300 --> 00:32:58.150
Okay.

00:32:58.360 --> 00:32:59.710
Put your hand through.

00:33:00.960 --> 00:33:02.030
Come on.

00:33:02.880 --> 00:33:03.720
There you go.

00:33:11.550 --> 00:33:12.200
Cheng Ken.

00:33:13.120 --> 00:33:14.250
Do you recognize us?

00:33:14.640 --> 00:33:16.440
We suspect you're involved in a case.

00:33:16.440 --> 00:33:18.400
We're conducting
a legal search of your residence.

00:33:18.400 --> 00:33:19.830
We hope you'll cooperate.

00:33:19.830 --> 00:33:20.550
Okay.

00:33:25.670 --> 00:33:26.920
How do you turn it?

00:33:30.590 --> 00:33:32.200
It's backwards.

00:33:34.150 --> 00:33:34.980
Almost done?

00:33:36.900 --> 00:33:37.530
Zhang Yan.

00:33:38.240 --> 00:33:39.100
That's enough.

00:33:41.240 --> 00:33:42.100
Find anything?

00:33:42.720 --> 00:33:43.440
No.

00:33:44.310 --> 00:33:45.510
Alright, head back to the bureau first.

00:33:45.510 --> 00:33:46.590
We'll ask a few questions,

00:33:46.590 --> 00:33:47.510
then we'll be back.

00:33:47.510 --> 00:33:48.000
Let's go. Move out.

00:33:48.000 --> 00:33:48.750
Good work.

00:33:49.000 --> 00:33:49.510
Bye.

00:33:51.920 --> 00:33:53.000
We'll just

00:33:53.200 --> 00:33:54.200
ask you a few simple questions.

00:33:54.200 --> 00:33:54.790
Okay.

00:33:55.830 --> 00:33:56.720
Go inside.

00:33:56.720 --> 00:33:58.250
Let me talk to the officers.

00:34:06.440 --> 00:34:07.350
On the evening of the 20th last month,

00:34:07.350 --> 00:34:09.150
where were you between 6 and 8 PM?

00:34:11.360 --> 00:34:12.150
I can't remember clearly.

00:34:12.150 --> 00:34:15.000
But I should have been home
with my kid that night,

00:34:15.000 --> 00:34:17.510
Since I got fired
from the factory earlier,

00:34:18.650 --> 00:34:21.380
I usually went out during the day
to look for work.

00:34:21.710 --> 00:34:22.920
Where did you go that afternoon?

00:34:22.920 --> 00:34:24.520
Looking for work too, right?

00:34:24.800 --> 00:34:25.510
Which day's afternoon?

00:34:25.510 --> 00:34:26.150
The 20th.

00:34:27.400 --> 00:34:28.230
What day of the week was the 20th?

00:34:28.230 --> 00:34:28.960
Friday.

00:34:30.360 --> 00:34:31.030
I remember it.

00:34:31.030 --> 00:34:32.710
That Friday, I was...

00:34:33.550 --> 00:34:34.920
I went out in the morning

00:34:34.920 --> 00:34:36.840
to the job market.

00:34:37.150 --> 00:34:38.610
I wanted to find a temp job,

00:34:39.510 --> 00:34:40.630
but didn't find one.

00:34:40.630 --> 00:34:42.400
I saw I still had some time after noon,

00:34:42.400 --> 00:34:44.760
so I went to see a friend
in the afternoon.

00:34:45.150 --> 00:34:45.590
What friend?

00:34:45.590 --> 00:34:46.520
What's his name?

00:34:47.000 --> 00:34:47.800
Cao Jinchuan.

00:34:47.810 --> 00:34:50.010
Since when is Cao Jinchuan your friend?

00:34:52.360 --> 00:34:53.360
Well, actually,

00:34:53.389 --> 00:34:54.850
we aren't really friends.

00:34:55.670 --> 00:34:57.930
I went to collect a debt
from him that day.

00:34:59.590 --> 00:35:01.960
Last time at the bar,

00:35:01.960 --> 00:35:02.670
as you know,

00:35:02.670 --> 00:35:04.270
he scammed me out of my money.

00:35:04.960 --> 00:35:06.840
You confiscated the money later,

00:35:06.840 --> 00:35:07.480
but I...

00:35:07.480 --> 00:35:08.540
I thought about it.

00:35:08.660 --> 00:35:09.620
I'm innocent.

00:35:09.640 --> 00:35:11.170
And I really need the money.

00:35:11.630 --> 00:35:12.230
I had no choice.

00:35:12.230 --> 00:35:13.670
I figured I'd try my luck,

00:35:13.670 --> 00:35:14.280
go find him,

00:35:14.280 --> 00:35:16.080
see if I could get the money back.

00:35:16.590 --> 00:35:17.510
Just over a thousand yuan,

00:35:17.510 --> 00:35:18.970
and he ran just seeing you?

00:35:19.840 --> 00:35:21.070
How do you know he ran?

00:35:21.870 --> 00:35:23.350
Answer my question first.

00:35:24.660 --> 00:35:25.760
Yes, he...

00:35:26.070 --> 00:35:27.550
When I called out to him,

00:35:27.550 --> 00:35:29.510
he stood up from his seat and ran.

00:35:29.510 --> 00:35:30.000
It startled me.

00:35:30.000 --> 00:35:30.550
I...

00:35:30.550 --> 00:35:31.710
I didn't know what was going on.

00:35:31.710 --> 00:35:33.110
So I quickly chased after him.

00:35:33.110 --> 00:35:34.670
I only found out after I caught him

00:35:34.670 --> 00:35:35.400
that he mistook me

00:35:35.400 --> 00:35:37.000
for some other creditor.

00:35:38.280 --> 00:35:39.840
So after you left the mahjong parlor,

00:35:39.840 --> 00:35:41.030
where did you run to?

00:35:41.760 --> 00:35:43.760
He ran out the back door of the parlor.

00:35:43.760 --> 00:35:44.800
He went out the back,

00:35:44.800 --> 00:35:46.230
along a small alley.

00:35:46.670 --> 00:35:48.710
That's where I cornered him.

00:35:48.710 --> 00:35:50.000
Well, not really cornered.

00:35:50.000 --> 00:35:51.070
We didn't get physical.

00:35:51.070 --> 00:35:52.070
We had a nice talk.

00:35:52.430 --> 00:35:53.960
I just told him my situation

00:35:54.230 --> 00:35:55.030
and how things were.

00:35:55.030 --> 00:35:55.710
Later,

00:35:56.360 --> 00:35:58.320
maybe he realized
I was having a hard time.

00:35:58.320 --> 00:35:59.720
So he gave the money back.

00:36:00.510 --> 00:36:01.710
Then I found

00:36:01.710 --> 00:36:04.070
a food stall nearby
and treated him to a meal.

00:36:04.070 --> 00:36:05.530
After the meal, we went our separate ways.

00:36:05.530 --> 00:36:06.930
I haven't seen him since.

00:36:08.920 --> 00:36:11.320
Why? Did something happen to Cao Jinchuan?

00:36:11.770 --> 00:36:12.770
Why do you ask?

00:36:16.510 --> 00:36:17.590
If nothing happened to him,

00:36:17.590 --> 00:36:19.590
you wouldn't be asking me like this.

00:36:20.290 --> 00:36:21.890
I really don't know him well.

00:36:21.960 --> 00:36:23.490
We only met those two times.

00:36:23.840 --> 00:36:26.190
If something really did happen to him,

00:36:26.330 --> 00:36:27.850
it's got nothing to do with me.

00:36:27.850 --> 00:36:29.450
We'll investigate that.

00:36:31.110 --> 00:36:31.630
By the way,

00:36:31.630 --> 00:36:32.860
do you know Li Baocai?

00:36:33.840 --> 00:36:34.900
Never heard of him.

00:36:35.360 --> 00:36:35.960
Never heard of him, huh?

00:36:35.960 --> 00:36:36.510
No.

00:36:37.280 --> 00:36:39.320
There's a scrap station in Wujing Village.

00:36:39.320 --> 00:36:40.190
Have you been there?

00:36:40.190 --> 00:36:41.120
Wujing Village?

00:36:41.510 --> 00:36:42.510
Never been there.

00:36:43.280 --> 00:36:44.110
That sure?

00:36:44.360 --> 00:36:46.360
Wujing Village isn't close to here.

00:36:47.920 --> 00:36:48.230
Okay.

00:36:48.230 --> 00:36:49.590
That's all we need from you.

00:36:49.590 --> 00:36:50.000
Okay.

00:36:50.190 --> 00:36:51.100
Would it be okay

00:36:51.880 --> 00:36:54.080
if we ask your daughter a few questions?

00:36:55.110 --> 00:36:56.880
Please leave her out of this.

00:36:56.880 --> 00:36:57.590
She's...

00:36:57.960 --> 00:36:58.550
still young,

00:36:58.550 --> 00:36:59.510
and her health isn't good.

00:36:59.510 --> 00:37:00.230
I don't want to scare her.

00:37:00.230 --> 00:37:01.110
Don't worry about that.

00:37:01.110 --> 00:37:02.710
We definitely won't scare her.

00:37:02.710 --> 00:37:03.920
Since she's a minor,

00:37:03.920 --> 00:37:05.190
we can't question her alone.

00:37:05.190 --> 00:37:06.110
As her guardian,

00:37:06.110 --> 00:37:07.480
you can just sit next to her.

00:37:07.480 --> 00:37:08.110
I can sit here?

00:37:08.110 --> 00:37:08.960
Sure. No problem.

00:37:08.960 --> 00:37:09.520
Okay.

00:37:10.280 --> 00:37:10.800
Jiajia.

00:37:10.880 --> 00:37:11.550
Jiajia.

00:37:12.110 --> 00:37:12.710
Come here.

00:37:14.800 --> 00:37:15.440
It's okay.

00:37:15.530 --> 00:37:17.790
They just want to ask you a few questions.

00:37:17.870 --> 00:37:19.130
Jiajia, let me ask you.

00:37:19.590 --> 00:37:21.590
What does Dad do at home every night?

00:37:22.440 --> 00:37:24.030
He cooks dinner and we eat.

00:37:24.030 --> 00:37:26.030
He watches TV with me and goes to bed.

00:37:27.110 --> 00:37:28.960
Is Dad home every night?

00:37:29.190 --> 00:37:30.510
Pretty much.

00:37:31.440 --> 00:37:32.840
On the 20th of last month,

00:37:33.670 --> 00:37:34.710
was Dad home?

00:37:35.510 --> 00:37:36.710
That was too long ago.

00:37:36.760 --> 00:37:37.920
I forgot.

00:37:39.070 --> 00:37:41.480
It's been so long.
You can't remember, right?

00:37:41.480 --> 00:37:41.760
Okay.

00:37:41.760 --> 00:37:42.480
Let me ask you this.

00:37:42.480 --> 00:37:44.680
Has anyone visited your home recently?

00:37:44.810 --> 00:37:46.040
Any strangers?

00:37:46.070 --> 00:37:47.590
Like young men or women?

00:37:47.880 --> 00:37:48.320
Yes.

00:37:49.000 --> 00:37:49.610
Who?

00:37:52.080 --> 00:37:52.520
Right.

00:37:53.040 --> 00:37:54.120
I did come once.

00:37:58.880 --> 00:37:59.330
Okay.

00:38:00.400 --> 00:38:02.260
I'm going to show you some photos.

00:38:04.230 --> 00:38:04.880
Look at this one.

00:38:04.880 --> 00:38:07.140
Have you seen this girl in these clothes?

00:38:09.150 --> 00:38:10.080
Look carefully.

00:38:11.110 --> 00:38:12.510
You haven't seen her, have you?

00:38:12.510 --> 00:38:13.360
No.

00:38:14.110 --> 00:38:14.760
Okay.

00:38:17.740 --> 00:38:19.200
Look at another one for me.

00:38:20.280 --> 00:38:21.510
Small packets like this

00:38:21.510 --> 00:38:22.590
filled with powder.

00:38:22.590 --> 00:38:23.650
Have you seen them?

00:38:25.190 --> 00:38:26.320
Or anything similar?

00:38:26.320 --> 00:38:27.110
No.

00:38:28.250 --> 00:38:30.580
You're sure you haven't seen this, right?

00:38:33.300 --> 00:38:34.220
Last one.

00:38:35.030 --> 00:38:36.360
Do you know this person?

00:38:45.620 --> 00:38:46.280
Look closely.

00:38:46.280 --> 00:38:47.630
Isn't that Jiang?

00:38:49.280 --> 00:38:50.590
It's Jiang.

00:38:50.770 --> 00:38:52.290
We're good friends.

00:38:53.270 --> 00:38:54.940
Jiang is your friend, right?

00:38:55.230 --> 00:38:56.230
They were in the same ward.

00:38:56.230 --> 00:38:57.960
That kid was seriously ill too.

00:38:59.030 --> 00:38:59.440
Okay.

00:38:59.740 --> 00:39:00.260
Okay.

00:39:00.320 --> 00:39:01.150
I have no more questions.

00:39:01.150 --> 00:39:02.470
Thanks for your cooperation.

00:39:02.470 --> 00:39:03.510
Say "you're welcome."

00:39:03.510 --> 00:39:04.440
You're welcome.

00:39:04.480 --> 00:39:05.880
That's all for today.

00:39:05.880 --> 00:39:06.150
Okay.

00:39:06.150 --> 00:39:07.230
And for the time being,

00:39:07.230 --> 00:39:08.880
don't leave Nuanfeng County.

00:39:08.880 --> 00:39:09.190
Okay.

00:39:09.190 --> 00:39:10.590
We'll come find you
if we have more questions.

00:39:10.590 --> 00:39:11.190
Anytime.

00:39:11.480 --> 00:39:12.360
Thank you for your time.

00:39:12.360 --> 00:39:12.970
No problem.

00:39:12.970 --> 00:39:14.430
Sorry for disturbing you.

00:39:14.550 --> 00:39:15.440
Bye, Jiajia.

00:39:15.490 --> 00:39:16.190
Say goodbye.

00:39:16.190 --> 00:39:16.920
Goodbye.

00:39:19.030 --> 00:39:20.070
Take care, Officer Jin.

00:39:20.070 --> 00:39:20.440
Bye.

00:39:20.440 --> 00:39:21.570
No need to see us out.

00:39:31.430 --> 00:39:32.150
Go play.

00:39:59.590 --> 00:40:01.000
Jiajia and Xue Jiang

00:40:01.000 --> 00:40:02.230
stayed in the same ward.

00:40:02.230 --> 00:40:04.090
They definitely know each other.

00:40:04.280 --> 00:40:05.800
But when she answered
your question just now,

00:40:05.800 --> 00:40:06.680
she clearly hesitated.

00:40:06.680 --> 00:40:07.680
Something's off.

00:40:08.670 --> 00:40:09.400
Here you are.

00:40:09.480 --> 00:40:09.940
Thanks.

00:40:10.190 --> 00:40:11.120
You're welcome.

00:40:11.360 --> 00:40:12.000
Look.

00:40:12.710 --> 00:40:14.640
When I showed her the photo just now

00:40:14.890 --> 00:40:16.520
and asked if she knew him,

00:40:17.320 --> 00:40:17.920
she didn't know how to answer.

00:40:17.920 --> 00:40:19.120
She looked at her dad.

00:40:19.670 --> 00:40:20.710
But when I asked her

00:40:20.710 --> 00:40:21.960
about the case earlier,

00:40:21.960 --> 00:40:22.480
she didn't look at him at all.

00:40:22.480 --> 00:40:23.800
She answered fluently.

00:40:23.800 --> 00:40:24.510
It shows

00:40:24.530 --> 00:40:26.530
they prepared for those questions.

00:40:26.670 --> 00:40:27.400
At the very least,

00:40:27.400 --> 00:40:28.660
she knew how to answer.

00:40:29.440 --> 00:40:30.400
Which tells us one thing:

00:40:30.400 --> 00:40:32.400
Cheng Ken
is definitely hiding something.

00:40:32.400 --> 00:40:33.400
That's for sure.

00:40:35.840 --> 00:40:38.630
So Jiajia has seen
the girl from the hotel?

00:40:39.320 --> 00:40:40.320
I'd bet on it.

00:40:40.960 --> 00:40:43.220
Which means Cheng Ken is the man in black.

00:40:44.060 --> 00:40:46.480
When we brought Cheng Ken
and Cao Jinchuan back from the bar,

00:40:46.480 --> 00:40:47.880
I noticed Cheng Ken was missing a sock

00:40:47.880 --> 00:40:49.000
at some point.

00:40:49.440 --> 00:40:51.030
I suspected he had drugs on him

00:40:51.030 --> 00:40:51.930
and threw them away on the way,

00:40:51.930 --> 00:40:53.010
but I had no proof.

00:40:53.430 --> 00:40:54.840
You never told me that.

00:40:54.870 --> 00:40:56.600
I only suspected it at the time.

00:40:56.800 --> 00:40:58.150
But looking at it now,

00:40:58.230 --> 00:41:00.870
he didn't go to Cao Jinchuan to buy drugs.

00:41:00.920 --> 00:41:02.960
He went to sell the drugs
he got from Yuelai Hotel

00:41:02.960 --> 00:41:03.780
to him.

00:41:07.710 --> 00:41:08.480
Look.

00:41:09.670 --> 00:41:11.330
After Cheng Ken got the drugs,

00:41:11.440 --> 00:41:13.550
he definitely wanted to sell them, right?

00:41:13.550 --> 00:41:15.180
So he went to Cao Jinchuan.

00:41:15.210 --> 00:41:17.040
But something went down

00:41:17.510 --> 00:41:18.800
between Cao Jinchuan and Li Baocai.

00:41:18.800 --> 00:41:20.510
Maybe an unfair split of the loot,

00:41:20.510 --> 00:41:21.510
or maybe Li Baocai

00:41:21.510 --> 00:41:22.960
didn't want to sell real drugs.

00:41:22.960 --> 00:41:24.220
Anything is possible.

00:41:25.110 --> 00:41:26.030
So Cao Jinchuan

00:41:26.510 --> 00:41:28.040
ended up killing Li Baocai.

00:41:28.100 --> 00:41:29.160
If that's the case,

00:41:29.430 --> 00:41:31.360
could Cheng Ken be his accomplice?

00:41:32.430 --> 00:41:33.760
But these are all just speculations.

00:41:33.760 --> 00:41:34.860
We have no evidence.

00:41:34.860 --> 00:41:36.370
Where is the girl from the hotel?

00:41:36.370 --> 00:41:37.500
Neither of us knows.

00:41:37.570 --> 00:41:39.370
Why did she leave with Cheng Ken?

00:41:40.340 --> 00:41:42.630
What's the relationship
between Cheng Ken and Lv Deli?

00:41:42.630 --> 00:41:44.090
Is he working for Ding Lai?

00:41:44.800 --> 00:41:46.760
And no drugs were found
in Cheng Ken's home.

00:41:46.760 --> 00:41:48.290
Who did he give the drugs to?

00:41:48.760 --> 00:41:49.560
Cao Jinchuan?

00:41:51.120 --> 00:41:53.050
You're firing too many questions.

00:41:53.630 --> 00:41:54.670
Anyway,

00:41:54.670 --> 00:41:56.730
if Cheng Ken wanted to sell the drugs,

00:41:56.760 --> 00:41:58.030
he'd have to get paid, right?

00:41:58.030 --> 00:41:59.670
The money would have to go into a bank.

00:41:59.670 --> 00:42:00.800
Check his bank account.

00:42:00.800 --> 00:42:01.550
Hurry up and eat.

00:42:01.550 --> 00:42:02.410
Let's go check.

00:42:11.590 --> 00:42:12.590
Just as expected.

00:42:13.760 --> 00:42:15.820
We dealt with Cao Jinchuan very well.

00:42:16.510 --> 00:42:18.240
If the cops had found anything,

00:42:18.760 --> 00:42:20.090
you'd be in cuffs by now.

00:42:21.900 --> 00:42:23.830
But they're faster than I thought.

00:42:25.510 --> 00:42:27.030
They've already connected me

00:42:27.030 --> 00:42:28.290
to that batch of drugs.

00:42:33.840 --> 00:42:35.300
Xiaoya and I need to leave.

00:42:35.590 --> 00:42:36.550
I'll give you the money before we go.

00:42:36.550 --> 00:42:37.550
No, no.

00:42:38.420 --> 00:42:40.670
Xiaoya was right the other day.

00:42:43.150 --> 00:42:44.150
I've been thinking.

00:42:44.150 --> 00:42:46.000
If we're talking long-term,

00:42:47.250 --> 00:42:49.180
the money we make now isn't enough.

00:42:57.800 --> 00:43:00.030
Cheng Ken's bank account is spotless.

00:43:00.280 --> 00:43:02.000
It's so clean I want to donate to him.

00:43:02.000 --> 00:43:02.710
Donate some to me too.

00:43:02.710 --> 00:43:04.190
I'm pretty broke myself.

00:43:06.070 --> 00:43:07.060
Let's go over it again.

00:43:07.060 --> 00:43:08.430
We'll find a clue.

00:43:09.880 --> 00:43:10.880
No matter what,

00:43:11.400 --> 00:43:13.200
anyone involved in drug dealing

00:43:13.670 --> 00:43:14.930
is beyond redemption.

00:43:19.740 --> 00:43:30.400
[Next Episode Preview]